node.text: Overwhelmed and grateful for the last couple of days seeing my vision for @roseinc come to life in stores and online. Thank you to everyone for all your sweet messages and support, to my retail partners @sephora and @spacenk and my incredible team for making my dreams come true. Here’s to an exciting new chapter! 🤍
